9. Business Rules
Every clinic is an independent tenant.
Clinic users cannot access another clinic's data.
Every appointment belongs to one clinic.
Every patient belongs to one clinic in the MVP.
A doctor cannot have overlapping appointments.
Appointment slots must be validated before confirmation.
Payment status must be verified before marking an invoice as paid.
Every consultation must be linked to an appointment.
Every lab report must be linked to a consultation or lab order.
All sensitive operations must be audited.
