Document Summary

This document defines what Clinora must achieve from a business perspective. It does not describe detailed screen designs, APIs, database schemas, or implementation details. Those belong in later documents such as the Product Requirements Documents (PRDs), Architecture Documents, API Specifications, and Sprint Plans.
